Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:34.56,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Eu sinto a natureza respirando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:41.42,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}em todo o meu corpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:48.04,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Continuando de muito tempo atrás,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:54.70,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}uma melodia infinita.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:24:03.90,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}O vento, o mar e o céu me chamam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:10.25,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Sinta o universo, não há fim para este universo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:16.97,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}como minha guitarra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:24.01,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Sinta o universo, a eternidade está bem aqui,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.01,0:24:39.06,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}O futuro brilha, então não preciso de coisas como o céu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:51.45,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Sinto que vou explodir, me deixe livre.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:25:04.94,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Eu gritarei para o outro lado do céu, eu deixo você livre
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.44,0:25:14.98,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Oh, agora a batida rugirá,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.98,0:25:18.08,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Nós vamos ser livres!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.70,0:25:24.95,Feel UniverseENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.5}Uau, nós vamos ser livres!
